comments: Burks (GSW) makes contact to the body of Payton (NYK) on the drive.
Robinson III (GSW) makes contact to the arm of Morris Sr. (NYK) during his shooting motion that affects his jump shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes clean contact to dislodge the ball prior to making incidental body contact with Chriss (GSW).
Chriss (GSW) makes marginal contact with Payton (NYK) after the steal and doesn't affect his ability to maintain control of the ball.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes marginal contact with Robinson III (GSW) at the end of his drive and does not affect his ability to defend.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Payton's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact.
Russell (GSW) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Payton (NYK) makes marginal contact with Russell (GSW) at the end of his drive and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Replay review of the foul called on Barrett (NYK) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
Burks (GSW) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Trier (NYK) makes marginal contact with Russell (GSW) during the inbound and doesn't affect his FOM.
Green (GSW) makes clean contact with the ball during Trier's (NYK) drive.
Chriss (GSW) makes marginal body contact with Payton (NYK) after he has secured the rebound.
Green (GSW) makes clean contact with the ball prior to making marginal contact with Payton's (NYK) arm.
Russell (GSW) makes contact to the arm of Payton (NYK) during the drive but the contact is marginal, and does not cause him to lose possession of the ball.
Burks (GSW) makes contact to the body of Payton (NYK) during the drive but does not affect his SQBR.
Burks (GSW) gathers on his right foot and takes two legal steps.
Robinson III (GSW) makes incidental contact as he legally contests Morris Sr.'s (NYK) jump shot attempt. The contact is initiated by Morris Sr.'s leg extension.
Robinson (NYK) and Burks (GSW) engage in incidental foot contact during Burks' drive.
Chriss (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the play at the basket by Randle (NYK) and cleanly blocks the dunk attempt.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with Morris Sr. (NYK) and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Russell (GSW) commits a take foul on Morris Sr. (NYK).
Robinson III (GSW) commits a take foul on Morris Sr. (NYK).
Robinson (NYK) makes clean contact to the ball during Robinson III's (MIN) jump shot attempt.
